      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 mb-10">描述问题，AI 自动诊断修复，不解决不收费</p>
      <div id="download" class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-12">
        <a href="#" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition">💻 Windows 下载</a>
        <a href="#" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-gray-800 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg hover:bg-gray-900 transition">🍎 macOS 下载</a>
