          <p class="text-gray-600">用自然语言描述问题，AI 理解并分析</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 hover:bg-blue-50 transition">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🔍</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">远程诊断</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">AI 自动检测电脑问题，无需专业知识</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 hover:bg-blue-50 transition">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🛠️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">一键修复</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">发现问题立即修复，省时省心</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 hover:bg-blue-50 transition">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🛡️</div>
