          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">下载安装</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">下载并安装 Jpair</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mx-auto mb-4">💬</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-blue-600 font-bold mb-2">Step 2</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">描述问题</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">用自然语言描述电脑问题</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mx-auto mb-4">🔍</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-blue-600 font-bold mb-2">Step 3</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">AI 诊断</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">授权后 AI 自动检测修复</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mx-auto mb-4">✅</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-blue-600 font-bold mb-2">Step 4</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">问题解决</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">确认解决才收费</p>
        </div>
